results.description:
White Rock lake, Winfrey Point
This was a new species of wasp for me & once again I found it on Queen Anne's lace.  The yellow on the face, in a V shape, identifies the species.  A male.  Bugguide confirms the id here:  https://bugguide.net/node/view/1472203
